data.description: GORGEOUS MOUNTAIN RETREAT ON 37 acres with BREATHTAKING VIEWS of rock formations, mountains, fields, and all types of wildlife. This 3 Bedroom 2 Bathroom LOG CABIN oozes charm of a bygone era while retaining modern day comforts like on demand hot water, etc. Living room featuress vaulted ceilings, stone surround fireplace & custom built shelves lending a cozy vibe with endless views from every window. Farmhouse style kitchen features a large copper sink, teak hardwood floors, granite counters island & breakfast bar, gas oven. Dining area walks out to a huge trex deck to enjoy your coffee, BBQ, or a glass of wine while you soak up the beautiful scenery, wildlife & peace. Primary bedroom offers a private retreat with a built in fireplace & sitting area, office nook, and new bathroom. Separate bonus room off the master is currently used as a gym but could also be a craft room, nursery, etc. Two other bedrooms are generously sized and share the cleverly designed full bath. Concrete patio off the Primary bedrom is wired for a hot tub. The yard is fenced around the side and back of the home for kids or pets. Outbuildings include a shed, fenced area for livestock & chicken coop plus a 40 x 14 Greenhouse with a cistern to easily water your garden. Large sections of the land have been cleared to have livestock, build a barn, garage, etc. Enjoy the fire pit area for star gazing! A seasonal stream runs through the lower end of property.
